rusians!]] in the category of \u201cMain Musical Events of the Year\u201d)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://budzma.by/news/halownyya-padzyei-hoda-pa-vyersii-budzma-byelarusami.html|title=\u0413\u0430\u043b\u043e\u045e\u043d\u044b\u044f \u043f\u0430\u0434\u0437\u0435\u0456 \u0433\u043e\u0434\u0430 \u043f\u0430 \u0432\u0435\u0440\u0441\u0456\u0456 \"\u0411\u0443\u0434\u0437\u044c\u043c\u0430 \u0431\u0435\u043b\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0441\u0430\u043c\u0456!\"|last=|first=|date=2015-12-24|publisher=[[Budzma Belarusians!]]|language=be|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925062723/https://budzma.by/news/halownyya-padzyei-hoda-pa-vyersii-budzma-byelarusami.html|archive-date=2019-09-25|access-date=2019-09-25}}</ref>\n* {{ill|Belsat Music Live|be|Belsat Music Live}} (author: Siarhei Budkin) (The Adami Media Prize-2018, Special Mention in the category of \u201cTV Entertainment\u201d)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adamimediaprize.eu/news/2018/12/5/six-competition-participants-win-adami-media-prize|title=ADAMI Media Prize announces Its six winners!|last=|first=|date=|website=Adami Media Prize for Cultural Diversity in Eastern Europe|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925061752/https://www.adamimediaprize.eu/news/2018/12/5/six-competition-participants-win-adami-media-prize|archive-date=2019-09-25|access-date=2019-09-25}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [[RSS]]-[http://www.tuzinfm.by/rss.html feed]\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8nwc8bbgQxA&list=PLdQABAxpFtAMFr_s4Fe0Y6WHOZlCjATE7 Belsat Music Live playlist (YouTube)]\n\n[[Category:Internet properties established in 2003]]\n[[Category:Media companies of Belarus]]\n[[Category:Media in Minsk]]\n[[Category:Belarusian news websites]]\n[[Category:2003 establishments in Belarus]]\n[[Category:Publications established in 2003]]\n[[Category:Belarusian music websites]]\n", "name_user": "John B123", "label": "safe", "comment": "Changed depreciated cite